{"tid":137784,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[無恥!] Intel 試圖操控 AMD 評測成績","createTime":"2017-02-28T05:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T11:33:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"facc8e1c511a6872946e4b3b6fa8266c3193b213","tid":137784,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>Intel 試圖影響 AMD Ryzen 的評測？<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.coolaler.com/threads/intel-amd-ryzen.342819/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fthreads%2Fintel-amd-ryzen.342819%2F&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6544fa49\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.coolaler.com/threads/intel-amd-ryzen.342819/</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\nAMD Ryzen 因為還在NDA中，目前還未看到有公開的完整測試，應該有部分媒體已經拿到處理器，甚至可能已經測好了等待解禁發布，不過有爆料稱 Intel 「關切」了媒體對於 Ryzen 的評測。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/17/02/amd_ryzen_ppt_7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F17%2F02%2Famd_ryzen_ppt_7.jpg&h=a3b6104e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTweaktown 爆料稱 Semi Accurate 的創辦人 Charlie Demerjian 最近收到 Intel 公關公司關切的郵件，表示在評測 Ryzen 之前先打給我們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n一般在產品發布之前，尤其是 CPU，各家媒體或網站除了收到處理器之外，還會有一些相關的技術文件，裡面可能會有一些測試指導方針或跑分建議，教你怎麼樣發揮他們家處理器最大的效能，這些是常情，畢竟優勢要體現出來，不過對手出 CPU，卻指導媒體要如何測試這倒是罕見。"},{"pid":"0b0a4579267efb5c9277851b3212ac6bf03da264","tid":137784,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肉撚酸<br />\n不過繼續用煙頭"},{"pid":"4132a5bfcc053657c562abff776808e8baf78dc